--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f832b14936fc2048824d9308b14ded6, type: 3}
  m_Name: Has she ever bullied the shit out of you
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  allLines:
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I\u2019ve heard sisters always tend to be amazing. Do you have like
      a memory of her bullying you straight into the ground? "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: '*laughs* Oh where should I even begin? There was this one time I had
      a little accident...

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'What kind of accident?

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Okay promise not to laugh, I was like 12. Shit like that never happens
      anymore, like, obviously it doesn\u2019t. And like I had the right to, I was
      sick with a stomach bug.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Did you shit yourself?

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: '...yeah.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Okay, you know what, it happens. Continue.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'I had stolen her console the week before and apparently she found
      it in my room the morning of the... event.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'The shitting event, okay.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Don\u2019t say it like that- Anyways, it happened at school but thankfully
      I made it to the bathroom before anyone saw. It was during class hours and
      suddenly, someone barged into the bathroom\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'It was her, apparently she came to confront me about it but then I
      made the mistake of being vulnerable and just told her about the situation
      I was in.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Oh no...

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Yeah so before I even knew she was angry with me, she went on to tell
      everyone in my year that I was in the bathroom with my pants covered in shit.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: '*chuckles* Ohohoh nooo that is evil.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'And then every guy in my year piled into the bathroom. There was a
      whole crowd waiting to see my skid mark.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I\u2019m guessing you never stole her stuff again.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'For a while, yeah. Then I got smart about it. She sounds absolutely
      evil when I tell it like this but believe me, I had it coming.

      

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Oh I don\u2019t feel all that bad for you. I can tell you were a naughty
      kid.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Would it be inappropriate to say I\u2019m naughtier now?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Mm, not at all, unless the Chaperon minds it.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  nextScenario: {fileID: 0}
